      "title": "STIX and TAXII Protocol Stack",
      "type": "architecture",
      "description": "STIX is the data format (language) representing indicators, TTPs, campaigns, and courses of action. TAXII is the transport protocol (postal service) used to distribute STIX packages between producers and consumers."
